{
  "texts": [
    "Most of these experiments concentrated on learning superficial aspects, such as texture and pattern recognition, as described in 5, grey level co-occurrence matrix or local binary pattern 6.",
    "However, each tumor contains a variety of textures, shapes, and color distributions.",
    "As a result, while dealing with the issues posed by current WSI, the previously discussed solutions are frequently constrained.",
    "Today histopathology images are quite big, containing billions of pixels.",
    "These slides typically present high-level, complicated clinical aspects."
  ]
}